Bullet did as he was told and sat. "Thank you sir" the weak bot said. His
eyes remained face forward with a blank stare. Perceptor was at the moment
the bot in charge and nothing more mattered. Protocall stated that he treat
any bot in his unit with a higher rank than him with respect.
